PART 6: THE FIVE-FOLD WAY — n=5 AS UNIVERSAL FIXED POINT
======================================================================

  max_H(5) = 15
  T(5) = 15
  C(5,1)+C(5,3) = 15
  2^4-1 = 15
  F(5)*F(4) = 15
  All = 15? True

  Triangular AND Mersenne numbers: [1, 3, 15, 4095]
  (Ramanujan-Nagell related: k(k+1)/2 = 2^j - 1)

  phi^5 = 11.090170 = 5*phi + 3 = 11.090170
  phi^n = F(n)*phi + F(n-1):
    phi^3 = 2*phi + 1 = 4.236068
    phi^4 = 3*phi + 2 = 6.854102
    phi^5 = 5*phi + 3 = 11.090170
    phi^6 = 8*phi + 5 = 17.944272

